snippet.title: Cohabitation - Trailer (RPG Maker Horror Game)
snippet.description:
A trailer for my new RPG Maker horror puzzle game, Cohabitation. Play it here: https://algebrafalcon.itch.io/cohabitation

Made with the help of monom, Monty Bichouna, Eric Lujan, Helen Zhou, and Shannon Kong.
